4. defaultdict – Word Length Grouping
Given:
words = ["python","java","go","c","ruby","php"]
Group the words using defaultdict(list) based on their length.

from collections import defaultdict

words = ["python","java","go","c","ruby","php"]
d = defaultdict(list)

for w in words:
