7. deque – Sliding Window Sum
Given:
nums = [1,2,3,4,5,6]
window = 3
Using deque, calculate the sum of every sliding window of size 3.


from collections import deque

nums = [1,2,3,4,5,6]
k = 3
dq = deque(nums[:k])

print(sum(dq))
for i in range(k, len(nums)):
    dq.popleft()
    dq.append(nums[i])
    print(sum(dq))

